https://www.fossdex.com/new/deploying-full-stack-mern-application-on-an-nginx-vps/

Step 1: Set up your VPS:
    <sudo apt update>
    <sudo apt upgrade>
    <sudo apt install nginx>

Step 2: Set up FireWall:
    <apt install ufw>
    <ufw enable>
    <ufw allow "Nginx Full">

Step 2: Install Node:
    <sudo apt install nodejs>






